ppy-java uses.\n- Removed placeholder `Snappy_javaTest.java`.\n- Updated `tests/src/org.xerial.snappy/snappy-java/1.0.4.1/build.gradle`\n  - Adds `--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED` for the JVM test task.\n  - Adds `--enable-native-access=ALL-UNNAMED`.\n  - Propagates both flags to Native Image build args.\n\nNotes:\n- I did not edit any reachability metadata files.\n- I did not run tests, per instruction. \n- The bundled native library path is exercised; the system-library fallback branch depends on an externally installed `snappyjava` library on `java.library.path`, so I left that unsupported branch unforced.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b44f9dc1e8c1183016a3da9e4e1fc8190a884c808fe9aade2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2272, "output": 1188, "cacheRead": 45056, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 48516, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782426069263, "responseId": "resp_0b44f9dc1e8c1183016a3da9d5a3bc8190862bc206da2fb9cd"}}
